==概述==
[[File:Apple_Pro_Display_XDR_and_Mac_Pro_(2019_model)_-_2.jpg|thumb]]
[[File:VESA_Mount_Adapter.svg|thumb]]
Pro Display XDR包含6016×3384 6K解析度颜色校准的面板，其后盖有着与第三代Mac Pro相似的格子形状的散热孔。为了提高对比度和[[高動態範圍|HDR]]功能，它使用[[藍光LED|蓝色LED]]代替白色作为背光源，[[刷新率|刷新率]]高于显示器本身，并且包含“定制透镜和反射镜”系统。前面提到的晶格用作散热器：苹果公司表示，这种设计为显示器提供了足够的热管理，使其可以在整个螢幕上以1000[[坎德拉每平方米|尼特]]的亮度“无限期”运行，在温度低于25°C（77°F）的环境中最高可以达到1600尼特。该显示器可提供可选的激光蚀刻“纳米纹理”玻璃饰面，以减少[[眩光|眩光]]<ref name="verge info 1" /><ref name="engadget info 1" /><ref name="DT info 1">{{cite web|url=https://www.digitaltrends.com/computing/apple-pro-display-xdr-explained|title=XDR vs. HDR: Why Apple's new 1,000 nit 6K monitor is such a big deal|website=Digital Trends|date=June 3, 2019|access-date=June 4, 2019|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126030406/https://www.digitaltrends.com/computing/apple-pro-display-xdr-explained/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。纳米纹理版本需要显示器随附的定制“干抛光布”，以对其进行清洁<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theverge.com/2019/12/10/21009928/apples-pro-display-xdr-nano-texture-cloth-clean|title=Apple’s most expensive Pro Display XDR requires a special, Apple-made cloth to clean it|last=Peters|first=Jay|date=2019-12-10|website=The Verge|language=en|access-date=2019-12-11|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112022538/https://www.theverge.com/2019/12/10/21009928/apples-pro-display-xdr-nano-texture-cloth-clean|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 

這部顯示器的機背有一個[[Thunderbolt_3|Thunderbolt 3]]埠（USB-C接頭規格）與三個[[USB-C|USB-C]]埠。Thunderbolt 3與電腦連接以顯示畫面，雖然Mac與PC平台皆可連接使用，但一些軟體功能只支援[[macOS_Catalina|macOS Catalina 10.15.2]]或後續版本之作業系統。三個USB-C埠可用於充電或同步用<ref>{{cite web |title=Pro Display XDR - 技術規格 |url=https://www.apple.com/tw/pro-display-xdr/specs/ |publisher=Apple (台灣) |accessdate=2021-05-27 |archive-date=2021-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210524174017/https://www.apple.com/tw/pro-display-xdr/specs/ }}</ref>。

Apple的显示器VESA安装适配器使用磁性系统安装显示器。支架可以作为附件单独购买，即“ VESA安装适配器”或“ Pro Stand支架”。两者都使用专有的磁铁系统来固定显示器。Pro Stand可进行高度调节和旋转，并包括一个锁定开关，当螢幕有足够的间隙可旋转90度时，该锁定开关可释放旋转。螢幕中的传感器会自动将用户界面旋转为纵向模式<ref name="verge info 2">{{cite web|url=https://www.theverge.com/circuitbreaker/2019/6/3/18651001/apples-mac-pro-xdr-display-monitor-stand-expensive-dongle-not-included-wwdc-2019|title=Apple's $1,000 Pro Display XDR stand is the most expensive dongle ever|first=Chaim|last=Gartenberg|website=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|date=June 3, 2019|access-date=June 4, 2019|archive-date=2021-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206100518/https://www.theverge.com/circuitbreaker/2019/6/3/18651001/apples-mac-pro-xdr-display-monitor-stand-expensive-dongle-not-included-wwdc-2019|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="cnet info 1">{{cite web|url=https://www.cnet.com/news/mac-pros-crazy-expensive-pro-display-xdr-doesnt-even-come-with-a-stand|title=Mac Pro's crazy expensive Pro Display XDR doesn't even come with a stand|first=Patrick|last=Holland|website=[[CNET|CNET]]|date=June 3, 2019|access-date=June 4, 2019|archive-date=2019-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190604074014/https://www.cnet.com/news/mac-pros-crazy-expensive-pro-display-xdr-doesnt-even-come-with-a-stand/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。苹果与[[罗技|罗技]]合作开发了一个4K网络攝影機，该攝影機可以以磁性方式附着在螢幕顶部 <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theverge.com/circuitbreaker/2019/12/10/21007602/logitech-4k-pro-magnetic-webcam-apple-display-xdr-mac-pro|title=Logitech made a bespoke $200 magnetic 4K webcam for Apple’s Pro Display XDR|last=Gartenberg|first=Chaim|date=2019-12-10|website=The Verge|language=en|access-date=2019-12-11|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126171343/https://www.theverge.com/circuitbreaker/2019/12/10/21007602/logitech-4k-pro-magnetic-webcam-apple-display-xdr-mac-pro|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

